oc:kn_1710f99e a oc:CodePattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Beat/miss analysis writeup format" ;
    oc:directiveContent """■ **Revenue Beat by 3% Driven by Strong DTC Performance**

Revenue of $13.5B exceeded our estimate of $13.1B by $400M (3%) and consensus
of $13.2B by $300M (2%). The outperformance was driven primarily by [driver].
Management cited [factors] as key drivers.""" .

oc:kn_2aad2217 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When updating price target after earnings" ;
    oc:directiveContent "If estimates changed significantly (>5%), usually change the price target. If changed marginally (<5%), may maintain. If thesis strengthened/weakened, may change even without estimate change." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Price targets should reflect material changes in the investment thesis while avoiding noise from immaterial estimate movements." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_2ef230ee a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:KnownIssue ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When identifying the earnings period" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Companies use varied fiscal calendars (calendar, Nike May FY-end, Apple Sept FY-end, Walmart Jan FY-end). Search '[company] fiscal year calendar' to correctly interpret quarter labels." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Misinterpreting fiscal quarters leads to wrong YoY comparisons and incorrect analysis; never assume calendar quarters." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_4a9ea10f a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Prerequisite ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Before starting earnings analysis" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Requires web search capability to find latest earnings releases, SEC EDGAR filings, and earnings call transcripts. Must be able to access investor relations pages and financial data sources." .

oc:kn_5b9b5c02 a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Before any earnings analysis begins" ;
    oc:directiveContent "NEVER use earnings data from training knowledge — it is outdated. Always actively search for and retrieve the most recent earnings materials before starting analysis." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Training data has a knowledge cutoff that makes financial data stale; using outdated numbers produces inaccurate and misleading research reports." ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_5f240ace a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:SuccessIndicator ;
    oc:appliesToContext "During quality check before delivery" ;
    oc:directiveContent "A complete earnings update deliverable includes: (1) 8-12 page DOCX report, (2) 8-12 embedded charts, (3) beat/miss clearly quantified, (4) old vs. new estimates shown, (5) all figures sourced with clickable hyperlinks, (6) rating and price target explicitly addressed." ;
    oc:hasRationale "These elements constitute a complete, institutional-quality earnings update that meets professional equity research standards." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_815e1bec a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:PreFlightCheck ;
    oc:appliesToContext "After initial data collection, before analysis phase" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Before proceeding with analysis, verify: (1) today's date written down, (2) actively searched for 'latest earnings', (3) earnings release date found and within 3 months, (4) all materials show the same quarter, (5) transcript date matches release date ±1 day." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Mixed-quarter or outdated materials are the #1 source of errors in earnings analysis; this checklist prevents using stale or mismatched data." ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_81783724 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When gathering consensus estimates for beat/miss analysis" ;
    oc:directiveContent "All consensus estimates must be pre-earnings (before the release date), not post-earnings revisions. Verify the source date of consensus data." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Post-earnings consensus will reflect updated analyst estimates and make beat/miss comparisons meaningless." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_c18ab5a7 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Procedure ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Full earnings update workflow execution" ;
    oc:directiveContent "1. Check today's date → 2. Search for latest earnings (web search + IR site) → 3. Verify release date within 3 months → 4. Identify fiscal quarter → 5. Gather press release + 10-Q/10-K + transcript → 6. Verify all materials same quarter → 7. Extract key metrics (Revenue, GM, EBITDA, EPS) → 8. Analyze beat/miss with drivers → 9. Segment/margin/guidance analysis → 10. Update estimates and valuation → 11. Generate 8-12 charts → 12. Create DOCX report → 13. Quality check → 14. Deliver" ;
    oc:stepOrder 1 .

